text:
Hi,

We're excited to introduce you to a beginner level LLM project that will help you gain comprehensive understanding and practical experience in working with LLMs. From fundamental concepts to advanced techniques, this project covers it all, help you to leverage LLMs effectively for various tasks, including text generation and building knowledge-grounded applications.

Key Learnings:
* Understanding LLMs: Explore the inner workings of LLMs, including RNNs, transformers, attention mechanisms, and their applications.
* Prompt Engineering Techniques: Learn how to write specific instructions to guide LLMs in generating desired responses, using zero-shot, one-shot, and few-shot inferences.
* Fine-Tuning and PEFT: Learn full fine-tuning and Parameter Efficient Fine Tuning (PEFT) to adapt pre-trained models for specific tasks, with a focus on dialogue summarization.
* Model Evaluation: Learn to use ROUGE metrics to assess the performance of fine-tuned models.
* RLHF Concept: Understand the concept of Reinforcement Learning from Human Feedback and its implications in model refinement.
* Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG): Implement RAG using OpenAI's GPT-3.5 Turbo to develop a chatbot for online shopping, ensuring trustworthy and reliable responses through knowledge grounding.
* Development of Chatbot Application: Build a functional chatbot application for online shopping using RAG.

Here's what you can expect from our project-based LLMs learning roadmap  :
* Access to Projects: Gain unlimited access to our curated selection of projects, covering a wide range of topics and technologies.
* Guided Step by Step Video Walkthrough: Follow along with our industry expert instructors as they guide you through each project, providing detailed explanations and insights along the way.
* Downloadable Solution Code: Access downloadable solution code for each project, allowing you to study, analyze, and customize the code to suit your needs.
* Datasets and Documentation: Access to datasets and documentation for each project, enabling you to practice and experiment with real-world data scenarios

Get Access Now 

Best Regards,
Anjali from ProjectPro
